      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TICKETS (8) goes very well here starting six times for two wins and three minors. Hit the frame latest (25.77) when second at this track in a Grade 5. Appeals as a leading chance in this. HONEY STIRRER (3) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing second (25.56) and beaten a neck over 450m at this track. Well placed and gets her chance. ASTON EXCLUSIVE (2) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (26.11) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. The form out of last race has been strong. Should be about the mark. MY DEAR FRIEND (1) looks a chance coming off a five weeks layoff.",
